      • testCalculateScores

        public void testCalculateScores()
        Tests the calculateScores supposing not to have PublicObjectiveCards. The test suppose that Pippo has placed a blue die with value 6 in position [1][0] and that Pluto has placed a red die with value 5 in the same position. Pippo's score must be : 6 (value of the die of his private objective placed) - 19 (number of empty cells left) + 4 (number of tokens) Pluto's score must be : 5 (value of the die of his private objective placed) - 19 (number of empty cells left) + 4 (number of tokens) *
